ID: 1
Summary: Error in application when registering a new user
Steps to reproduce:
  1. Open the registration page on the website
  2. Enter username, email address and password
  3. Click on the "Register" button
Expected result: User is successfully registered and redirected to the login page
Actual result: The website displays an error message "Failed to register the user. Please try again later."
Severity: Critical
Priority: P0
Application version: 1.2.3
OS: Ubuntu 20.04
Additional details: The error occurs regardless of the browser and language used. Attempts to re-register have been unsuccessful.

Screenshot of the error is attached.


